{"tid":1787837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗爭者情緒受困靠藥物入睡","createTime":"2019-12-18T08:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T08:13:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12cacca08d5535e4eee14f391a1d284cffd2fb7b","tid":1787837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/YHDFFRO7RZPHHY6UEXALBHFSPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FYHDFFRO7RZPHHY6UEXALBHFSPA%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuocyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=737bb7f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FYHDFFRO7RZPHHY6UEXALBHFSPA%2F&h=cb5d21cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/YHDFFRO7RZPHHY6UEXALBHFSPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n抗爭者情緒受困靠藥物入睡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576601255_1457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576601255_1457.jpg&h=388b70e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為在台的抗爭者意志消沉，故設計師寫上心意卡鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】逆權運動持續半年，警方拘捕逾6,000名抗爭者，當中不乏濫捕個案，不少抗爭者因此避走台灣。正在台灣的抗爭者A君透過義務律師黃國桐表示，數月前以旅遊簽證到台灣逗留至今，一方面慶幸自己有機會到一個民主自由的地方，另一方面曾因對前路迷惘，加上身在香港戰場外的無力感，開始出現情緒困擾，甚至要靠藥物才能入睡。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社區放TG 「如攻擊市民」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生活漫無目的<br />\n<br />\n黃國桐昨日在台灣探望抗爭者，也有與A君見面。A君表示，因以旅遊簽證到台灣，所以不能工作，一直未能融入台灣社會，生活也變得漫無目的。他以往在港從事飲食業，希望在台灣能做回老本行，自力更生，不需成為台灣政府或其他人的負擔，也可重拾生活的動力。他希望可獲台灣政府發出工作證，在「保護傘」計劃下開設的早餐店工作，不需再靠別人供養，也對台灣社會有所貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳沛冰"},{"pid":"9d6ccc024646be3083bac51bde947cfe346ca2e4","tid":1787837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}